{"tid":1984854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧玲：曾國衛上位短期內目的係取消9月立法會選舉 成立臨立會2.0 長期協助中央落實全面答治權","createTime":"2020-04-22T17:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T03:06:20.000Z","uid":210495,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"159bffc5a6df32be07de1a5315db45fac27d5ef0","tid":1984854,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:44:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9hCB5Ljr1Ys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9hCB5Ljr1Ys&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=8f7ad6d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9hCB5Ljr1Ys</a><br />\n短期內要制止民主派拎到35+<br />\n9月<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔一定</span></span></strong>有選舉<br />\n<blockquote>李慧玲：立法會選舉有機會被取消 或復辟臨立會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1938829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1938829</a></blockquote><br />\n政府<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未刊憲</span></span></strong> 9月6號只係一個傳聞<br />\n<blockquote>推上熱門！政府企圖拖延公布立法會選舉日 一人一email要佢交日子出黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fkKgeS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fkKgeS</a></blockquote><br />\n當呢屆立法會期完結 就成立臨立會<br />\n可以立<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>勁辣版23條</strong></span></span><br />\n可以立香港版《解救人民與帝國苦難法》 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B1933%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B1933%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%258E%2588%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B3%2595&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=4fd7dbdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B1933%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A%E6%B3%95</a><br />\n立乜法都得<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">羅冠聰：北京啟動「攬炒」 郭榮鏗涂謹申梁耀忠將被DQ 九月選舉將大量DQ候選人甚至當選人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fpMswS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fpMswS</a><br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fb5ddff1a003007ec2f69ef639302147dc6b3611","tid":1984854,"uid":76591,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:46:40.000Z","msg":"取消又點？香港人返工大過天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dbc53aaf67ec402b6b23d6a50a59c3a57b2cb2","tid":1984854,"uid":257190,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:56:17.000Z","msg":"如果係咁，真係好事<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔洗爭，少左分裂不和嘅機會</span><br />\n同時令到d淺黃，同仲信議會有用嘅手足知道議會冇用<br />\n再可以係國際戰線上<span style=\"color: red;\">講香港同支那冇分別</span>，取消獨立關稅<br />\n都係果句，我最怕支共唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：9月一定要投票，唔經初選，反口嘅都唔會投"},{"pid":"c863f3c6b4a3ce48b6d8c604268bc6df7fed63dd","tid":1984854,"uid":320192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"67dbc53aaf67ec402b6b23d6a50a59c3a57b2cb2","tid":1984854,"uid":257190,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:56:17.000Z","msg":"如果係咁，真係好事<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔洗爭，少左分裂不和嘅機會</span><br />\n同時令到d淺黃，同仲信議會有用嘅手足知道議會冇用<br />\n再可以係國際戰線上<span style=\"color: red;\">講香港同支那冇分別</span>，取消獨立關稅<br />\n都係果句，我最怕支共唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：9月一定要投票，唔經初選，反口嘅都唔會投"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T18:00:19.000Z","msg":"叫多啲人用Twitter 仲好 <br />\n200萬入面應該有199萬係懶閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21895384b9ab504ae71effd1380f72fce6fb7bd1","tid":1984854,"uid":257190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c863f3c6b4a3ce48b6d8c604268bc6df7fed63dd","tid":1984854,"uid":320192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"67dbc53aaf67ec402b6b23d6a50a59c3a57b2cb2","tid":1984854,"uid":257190,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"